title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of sync
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported jar file for the second time (PA 8/17/01 2:03:29 PM).
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself. It should be excluded from the export process.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the project that contains the directory to export. 
2. Export the directory as a jar file. 
3. Place the exported jar file in the same directory. 
4. Overwrite the exported jar file with the same file for the second time. 
5. Observe the out of sync message.
